      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for a budget-conscious buyer. While the engine and transmission are fully operational and have been maintained for daily use, there are visible signs of wear both inside and out, including minor exterior scuffs and some upholstery aging. It has a high mileage but runs well for its age, making it a practical choice for a daily commuter.",
