    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily trips. It runs smoothly, looks great, and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner! If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s been well-loved, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
