    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 straight-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The high-revving valvetrain remains tight, with recent VANOS servicing and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis integrity under high lateral loads. Equipped with the factory M-Variable differential and a set of staggered Style 67 wheels, it offers the quintessential analog driving experience. The suspension geometry is well-sorted, and the braking system retains excellent initial bite and thermal management. A mechanically robust example for the driver who values engineering precision and telepathic steering feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
